Geometry Wars(Fake)
Demonstrated and thought by Dave Churchill - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL_xRyXins848nDj2v-TJYahzvs-XW9sVV

Steps:
1. Extract files from zip
2. Run the app Geometry-War

Note: Do not change anything else except
        Window 1250 650 60 *1* - that is toggle between 1-(Fullscreen) and 0.
      Make sure all files are in same location

Game has no menu or other scenes apart.
Sound was not included. Until I learn that I guess

Instructions
Movement - Arrow keys
Basic weapon - mouse left click
Special weapon - mouse right click
toggle special weapon - keyboard key C
Pause - keyboard key P
End - Keyboard key esc
